n", "last_modified": 1776506311, "replies": 82, "id": 1206847}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6e27/13a6/557_large.png?m=1747623425", "name": "life", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6e27/13a6/557_normal.png?m=1747623425", "title": "生活", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/life", "topics": 10631, "footer": "", "header": "生活中的技术讨论", "title_alternative": "Life", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6e27/13a6/557_mini.png?m=1747623425", "stars": 2279, "founder_id": 0, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 557, "parent_node_name": ""}, "member": {"id": 803946, "username": "Lini1122", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/Lini1122", "website": null, "twitter": null, "psn": null, "github": null, "btc": null, "location": null, "tagline": null, "bio": null, "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/cd12/514e/803946_mini.png?m=1776526132", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/cd12/514e/803946_normal.png?m=1776526132", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/cd12/514e/803946_large.png?m=1776526132", "avatar_xlarge": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/cd12/514e/803946_xlarge.png?m=1776526132", "avatar_xxlarge": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/cd12/514e/803946_xxlarge.png?m=1776526132", "avatar_xxxlarge": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/cd12/514e/803946_xxxlarge.png?m=1776526132", "created": 1776514165, "last_modified": 1776526132, "pro": 0}, "last_reply_by": "xiaohanliang", "last_touched": 1776563138, "title": "我妈逼迫我 23 年深圳买房，导致 3 年房子降价 100 万，加上 30 年利息亏损 180 万", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/1206894", "created": 1776521562, "deleted": 0, "content": "我的成长背景：\r\n\r\n我是男的。我家有爷爷奶奶，爸爸和妈妈，我弟（比我小 13 岁），叔叔，姥姥，大舅，小舅。\r\n\r\n我从小就是一个比较内向的人。从小我爸妈就把垃圾情绪发泄给我，导致我一直拉个脸，他们就会怒斥我，为什么老是拉个脸！！！！\r\n\r\n我爸从我小时就来到深圳，跟我大舅做吊车生意，算是给我大舅打工。我妈从我幼儿园到小学 5 年纪，之后就把我丢到我爷爷奶奶家了，她来深圳和我爸住一块了。我从此以后就寒暑假来深圳找我爸妈。\r\n\r\n到了深圳以后，就开始猛教训我，他们不是拉近和我的关系，而是一直让我做家务，一直训斥我，一直教育我，一直打压我说我是个废物。我很不明白，为什么对我态度这么差？好像我学习不好就对他们没用。", "content_rendered": "我的成长背景：<br /><br />我是男的。我家有爷爷奶奶，爸爸和妈妈，我弟（比我小 13 岁），叔叔，姥姥，大舅，小舅。<br /><br />我从小就是一个比较内向的人。从小我爸妈就把垃圾情绪发泄给我，导致我一直拉个脸，他们就会怒斥我，为什么老是拉个脸！！！！<br /><br />我爸从我小时就来到深圳，跟我大舅做吊车生意，算是给我大舅打工。我妈从我幼儿园到小学 5 年纪，之后就把我丢到我爷爷奶奶家了，她来深圳和我爸住一块了。我从此以后就寒暑假来深圳找我爸妈。<br /><br />到了深圳以后，就开始猛教训我，他们不是拉近和我的关系，而是一直让我做家务，一直训斥我，一直教育我，一直打压我说我是个废物。我很不明白，为什么对我态度这么差？好像我学习不好就对他们没用。", "last_modified": 1776521923, "replies": 80, "id": 1206894}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/e7b2/4b11/360_large.png?m=1670319927", "name": "windows", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/e7b2/4b11/360_normal.png?m=1670319927", "title": "Windows", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/windows", "topics": 4513, "footer": "", "header": "Windows, not walls.", "title_alternative": "Windows", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/e7b2/4b11/360_mini.png?m=1670319927", "stars": 1380, "founder_id": 0, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 360, "parent_node_name": "os"}, "member": {"id": 564593, "username": "HitmanT", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/HitmanT", "website": "", "twitter": null, "psn": null, "github": null, "btc": null, "location": "", "tagline": "", "bio": "", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/467e/1c7b/564593_mini.png?m=1775703758", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/467e/1c7b/564593_normal.png?m=1775703758", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/467e/1c7b/564593_large.png?m=1775703758", "avatar_xlarge": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/467e/1c7b/564593_xlarge.png?m=1775703758", "avatar_xxlarge": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/467e/1c7b/564593_xxlarge.png?m=1775703758", "avatar_xxxlarge": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/467e/1c7b/564593_xxxlarge.png?m=1775703758", "created": 1638923118, "last_modified": 1775703758, "pro": 0}, "last_reply_by": "sir283", "last_touched": 1776539267, "title": "windows 更新这么离谱吗", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/1206784", "created": 1776477009, "deleted": 0, "content": "本来电脑安装的是 win10 专业版。昨晚睡觉之前关机，发现有更新。顺手就点了更新并关机，结果早上一开机变成 win11le ???要不要这么不要脸", "content_rendered": "<p>本来电脑安装的是 win10 专业版。昨晚睡觉之前关机，发现有更新。顺手就点了更新并关机，结果早上一开机变成 win11le ???要不要这么不要脸</p>\n", "last_modified": 1776477009, "replies": 43, "id": 1206784}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/93d6/5641/1022_large.png?m=1524208255", "name": "ipv6", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/93d6/5641/1022_normal.png?m=1524208255", "title": "IPv6", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/ipv6", "topics": 161, "footer": "", "header": "互联网协议的最新版本，为网络上的每一台设备提供标识和定位。", "title_alternative": "IPv6", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/93d6/5641/1022_mini.png?m=1524208255", "stars": 246, "founder_id": 0, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 1022, "parent_node_name": "internet"}, "member": {"id": 239594, "username": "jacketma", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/jacketma", "website": "", "twitter": null, "psn": null, "github": null, "btc": null, "location": "", "tagline": "", "bio": "", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/a941f83ac4192740c2e1f95676ce23c5?s=24&d=retro", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/a941f83ac4192740c2e1f95676ce23c5?s=48&d=retro", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/a941f83ac4192740c2e1f95676ce23c5?s=73&d=retro", "created": 1499704166, "last_modified": 1770973638, "pro": 0}, "last_reply_by": "huanxianghao", "last_touched": 1776526577, "title": "IETF 推出 IPv8 协议， IPv6 说明是个草台班子", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/1206826", "created": 1776489454, "deleted": 0, "content": "IPv6 这么多年推不动，难道就没有人觉得 IPv6 协议丑陋无比吗，那一坨地址看着就不想用啊\r\n\r\n二十年了，IETF 终于醒悟了，改 IPv8 全面兼容 IPv4\r\n\r\nr.r.r.r.n.n.n.n 如果 r 全部为 0 ，自动识别为 IPv4\r\n\r\n终于看的顺眼了\r\n\r\nIPv6 说明世界真是个草台班子", "content_rendered": "<p>IPv6 这么多年推不动，难道就没有人觉得 IPv6 协议丑陋无比吗，那一坨地址看着就不想用啊</p>\n<p>二十年了，IETF 终于醒悟了，改 IPv8 全面兼容 IPv4</p>\n<p>r.r.r.r.n.n.n.n 如果 r 全部为 0 ，自动识别为 IPv4</p>\n<p>终于看的顺眼了</p>\n<p>IPv6 说明世界真是个草台班子</p>\n", "last_modified": 1776489454, "replies": 31, "id": 1206826}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c20a/d4d7/12_large.png?m=1751718333", "name": "qna", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c20a/d4d7/12_normal.png?m=1751718333", "title": "问与答", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/qna", "topics": 238238, "footer": "", "header": "<!--\r\n一个更好的世界需要你持续地提出好问题。\r\n-->", "title_alternative": "Questions and Answers", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c20a/d4d7/12_mini.png?m=1751718333", "stars": 4481, "founder_id": 0, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 12, "parent_node_name": "v2ex"}, "member": {"id": 433153, "username": "S1ngleton", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/S1ngleton", "website": "https://www.blog.lebear.com", "twitter": null, "psn": null, "github": null, "btc": null, "location": "", "tagline": "", "bio": "", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/aa6b26b490350af3246a10a04ad66a91?s=24&d=retro", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/aa6b26b490350af3246a10a04ad66a91?s=48&d=retro", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/aa6b26b490350af3246a10a04ad66a91?s=73&d=retro", "created": 1564547688, "last_modified": 1606228239, "pro": 0}, "last_reply_by": "likai", "last_touched": 1776528087, "title": "10 公里通勤摩托车选择", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/1206809", "created": 1776483735, "deleted": 0, "content": "目前看好了 豪爵 afr125 和铃木 uy125 ，但是\n\n- 豪爵发动机差一些，有前 abs\n- 铃木发动机好，但是没 abs 刹车软\n\n\n想问下大家有没有推荐的，以及原因？最好是很了解某一个车型\n\n本人的话：每目的主要单程 10 公里通勤，非常偶尔（一两个月一次）的近郊游玩，不上高速，属于安全为主，喜欢电动车的感觉但是续航焦虑。", "content_rendered": "目前看好了 豪爵 afr125 和铃木 uy125 ，但是<br /><br />- 豪爵发动机差一些，有前 abs<br />- 铃木发动机好，但是没 abs 刹车软<br /><br /><br />想问下大家有没有推荐的，以及原因？最好是很了解某一个车型<br /><br />本人的话：每目的主要单程 10 公里通勤，非常偶尔（一两个月一次）的近郊游玩，不上高速，属于安全为主，喜欢电动车的感觉但是续航焦虑。", "last_modified": 1776483735, "replies": 26, "id": 1206809}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6353/8fe6/519_large.png?m=1595507885", "name": "ideas", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6353/8fe6/519_normal.png?m=1595507885", "title": "奇思妙想", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/ideas", "topics": 6518, "footer": "", "header": "让你的创意在这里自由流动吧。", "title_alternative": "Ideas", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6353/8fe6/519_mini.png?m=1595507885", "stars": 3225, "founder_id": 0, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 519, "parent_node_name": "v2ex"}, "member": {"id": 156781, "username": "cufezhusy", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/cufezhusy", "website": "", "twitter": null, "psn": null, "github": null, "btc": null, "location": "", "tagline": "", "bio": "", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/b596/16fd/156781_mini.png?m=1768748652", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/b596/16fd/156781_normal.png?m=1768748652", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/b596/16fd/156781_large.png?m=1768748652", "avatar_xlarge": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/b596/16fd/156781_xlarge.png?m=1768748652", "created": 1453654810, "last_modified": 1768748652, "pro": 0}, "last_reply_by": "unco020511", "last_touched": 1776521997, "title": "如果我是个企业，可以用哪些方法对冲 token 价格上涨的风险？", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/1206837", "created": 1776493348, "deleted": 0, "content": "现在每个企业都在用 AI ，如果我是企业的 CFO ，我会想有没有什么办法对冲（或者锁定） token 价格上涨的风险？\r\n\r\n现在想到的办法有\r\n－ 与供应商签订长期合同，比如微软就可以提供固定 Token 价格的长期合同，风险是企业被锁定在单一的供应商上。\r\n－ 购买电力价格期货，假设 token 价格上涨的最大因素是电力价格。\r\n－ ？？\r\n\r\n\r\n我目前的几个疑问：\r\n\r\nToken / 推理成本到底更像什么？\r\n－ 大宗商品（电力）？\r\n－ 云资源（ AWS ）？\r\n－ 还是一种新的资产类别？\r\n有没有企业已经在做“系统性对冲”，而不是简单谈判价格？\r\n如果未来出现“算力期货”，它的标的应该如何定义？\r\n－ Token 数量？\r\n－ FLOPs ？\r\n－ 还是某种标准化模型调用？\r\n\r\n欢迎拍砖，尤其想听听：\r\n有没有人从 CFO / Treasury 角度真的在设计这类对冲策略？", "content_rendered": "现在每个企业都在用 AI ，如果我是企业的 CFO ，我会想有没有什么办法对冲（或者锁定） token 价格上涨的风险？<br /><br />现在想到的办法有<br />－ 与供应商签订长期合同，比如微软就可以提供固定 Token 价格的长期合同，风险是企业被锁定在单一的供应商上。<br />－ 购买电力价格期货，假设 token 价格上涨的最大因素是电力价格。<br />－ ？？<br /><br /><br />我目前的几个疑问：<br /><br />Token / 推理成本到底更像什么？<br />－ 大宗商品（电力）？<br />－ 云资源（ AWS ）？<br />－ 还是一种新的资产类别？<br />有没有企业已经在做“系统性对冲”，而不是简单谈判价格？<br />如果未来出现“算力期货”，它的标的应该如何定义？<br />－ Token 数量？<br />－ FLOPs ？<br />－ 还是某种标准化模型调用？<br /><br />欢迎拍砖，尤其想听听：<br />有没有人从 CFO / Treasury 角度真的在设计这类对冲策略？", "last_modified": 1776493720, "replies": 23, "id": 1206837}, {